Author: simplyskyla
Text: Please be careful. I went on for a year exactly like this and it just spiraled more and more out of control. You are in a healthy, low-end of normal BMI range. I get that it’s not enough right now but it won’t be enough when you get down to 140 either...or 130....or 125....it just keeps getting worse but you can’t stop because it’s become the norm and going back is unthinkable.
